Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I get carried away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have fought brilliantly by pushing Vox Aura’s abilities to its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Moid, and you have made a lasting impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ox what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the name of that Ovid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that’s its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t think it would be that easy to pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moves just the way I tell it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s red.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Tadokoro, the Fleet Captain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to conduct a briefing before your next mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next? There’s going to be more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I… go to the restroom first?
