Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Izo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t wait. Array’s Ovid is not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means one of us has to go down there and rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy Ovid signal wasn’t like anything we’ve ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that they brought out the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t overrule that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they already have the Vox,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s possible “Memoria” has been achieved as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they’ve found a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the more the reason for me to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m the best Ovid pilot in De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of the Vox to crush Le Garite is our destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time like now to gauge the power of the legendary weapon that will eventually become ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don’t come back, get out and save yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tricked. I was totally tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me that there was going to be a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she pretend to be my comrade just to lull me into piloting that Ox thingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were those memories false too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was real… I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it? I’m so confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! They’re all from Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what’s up?
