Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, one bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that your cousin beat that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing how it’s not moving, I guess it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your cousin actually manage to pilot that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she could only ride a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she actually got a scooter license.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not enough to pilot a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve spent five years trying to figure out the OOPArts with no success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet the guys here built a robot out of it in six months!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s got to be some secret to—!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please don’t leave me alone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you planning to do if Kyouno Madoka failed to activate Vox Aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who’ve achieved Memoria with the Vox become its one and only pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Vox Aura falls into enemy hands, as long as we safeguard Miss Kyouno Madoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have an even chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same can be said should their positions be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have accelerated her organic response with the Vox,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was risky, so I wanted to avoid doing so if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn’t really have a viable countermeasure in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad that thing actually moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also learned quite a bit thanks to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t give a damn about protecting this planet, inside that head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting the Vox equates to protecting Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose idea was it to make the Vox battle in the forefront?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons from Earth are useless against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don’t you take the Vox and get off this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Earth would fall under their sphere of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a future would be bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what now, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that kind of gamble work twice against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging solely from the performance of the craft, its power surpasses that of the enemy’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest depends on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we’ll just have to see where the wind takes us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one last question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the main force really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately. Right after the war on their side is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot has run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. I’m completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks similar…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it’s a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’s there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! I’m…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.77,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?! {overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot… or… rather…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Kyouno Madoka. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Miss Muginami…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I’m going to look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait now…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I wasn’t trying to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right. I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wish I could help more, instead of forcing everything onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I could only fly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way I’m going to fit into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you do it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure. Let’s see where the wind takes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now listen calmly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An enemy has appeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Presently, its location is 100 klicks southeast of Oshima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s heading this way at mach 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like it’ll engage us in three minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will control the craft during Piercer Mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All you have to do is sit tight, just like last time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that last crash an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she’s referring to what triggered the Form Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn’t an accident. It was planned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we’re going to do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Correct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyouno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of our planet rests in your hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We’re counting on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t handle that kind of pressure right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole planet? I’ve never even been to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing Vox Aura A.I. Remote System check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Codes 1 through 11 are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pilot’s heart rate, blood pressure, respiratory rate… all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening barrier wall number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit two is approaching quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Vox Aura will engage the enemy… in approximately 100 seconds. {overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A.I. Remote Systems are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No effect on the Vox System.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.78,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuttle locks are open. {overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check complete. All systems go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m starting to get really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox System is silent like the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hope she pulls through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Ovid signal…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not Array’s, so that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should see the enemy straight ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it… a black one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We’re going in head on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with it… charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don’t know, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox System suddenly started up and is overriding the A.I. Remote!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me she can control it in Piercer Mode as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the girl really is a perfect match for Vox Aura, isn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be concerned, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All stations, prepare for attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn’t it either! This place is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re the real deal, then let’s see how you’ll handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura’s power grid is failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the status of the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her vital signs are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The craft, however, has shut down completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you handle it, my lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fear the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really accept the Vox in your current state?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Array lost to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no use! I can’t see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a crazy idea to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, a pilot…
