Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.43,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Rounded MT\b1\an8\c&HCECCB8&\fs72\fax0.02\bord18\blur3\3c&H545340&\pos(958.5,648)\frz346.613}Y{\3c&H565542&}o{\3c&H5E5C48&}u{\3c&H63614D&}k{\3c&H6B6955&}o {\3c&H6D6B56&}N{\3c&H746C57&}a{\3c&H75715A&}k{\3c&H79755D&}a{\3c&H7C7961&}i{\3c&H7F7C63&}z{\3c&H827D64&}u{\3c&H8A826A&}m{\3c&H928A72&}i{sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youko…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside a robot…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patching her through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait… You’re not surprised?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones work in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s that call coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within Pharos premises, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you piloting a robot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, one thing led to another, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I wanted to ask you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to me when I almost drowned ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I met this robot back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the enemy unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance from Vox Aura: 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s inside that black smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… of all the places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s a marine archeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s been snooping around ever since our foundation confiscated her research regarding Vox Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot’s cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one opposed to Kyouno Madoka piloting Vox Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moves exactly the way I want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared at first, but I got the hang of it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite fun, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meaning it’s not anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, after giving it some thought…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit two, distance from Vox Aura: 130!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems a lot of people are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}relying on me to pilot this robot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live up to their expectations as best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to disappoint anyone, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I started thinking about that, it stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who the hell do you think you are?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing’s not moving because you’re acting like you’re doing a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you have to feel grateful to them for letting you pilot that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But If you decided to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then stand by the decision you made!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that bothers you, then you should…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,quit the Jersey Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You’re so irritating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you’re right. You are absolutely right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off hearing that coming from you, Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It drives me nuts!{SHE HATES IT!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance from enemy unit: 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance: ten, nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.71,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight! Seven! {overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six! Five! Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox System online!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance to enemy unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unknown craft has broken through the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pincer attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirius, what are you—?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t sit back and watch this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we’re going to die, we’ll die together!
