Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to do it and I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’re going to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I make up my mind about doing, I go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s how I roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you’re in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Array?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Well, I’ve been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izo said that you suck.
